$$$R = \left[ {{V_{an}}\,\,{V_{bn}}\,\,{V_{cn}}} \right]\left[ {\matrix{
   0 &amp; {{1 \over {\sqrt 3 }}} &amp; { - {1 \over {\sqrt 3 }}}  \cr 
   { - {1 \over {\sqrt 3 }}} &amp; 0 &amp; {{1 \over {\sqrt 3 }}}  \cr 
   {{1 \over {\sqrt 3 }}} &amp; { - {1 \over {\sqrt 3 }}} &amp; 0  \cr 

 } } \right]\left[ {\matrix{
   {{i_a}}  \cr 
   {{i_b}}  \cr 
   {{i_c}}  \cr 

 } } \right],$$$
